            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hello, Pamela."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x42,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Why if it isn't Sophie. Welcome."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Wait just a minute. I'm almost done."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Oh, okay."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Sorry for the wait. What do you need today?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I was wondering if you had anything good, so I dropped by. Are you busy?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Well, I have to take care of the children, and also finish some church work."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Now that you mention it... You're doing a lot of work by yourself, Pamela."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "The priest has other important work to do, and not many people work at this church, so I can't help that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "But the children help me, so it isn't that bad."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x35,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Um, around when do you wake up every morning?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Let's see... Maybe around when the sun comes up?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "T-that early!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I got used to it really fast. Oh right, you said you wanted something, I'll get everything ready."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "(Pamela sure is a hard worker... I can learn something from her.)"
        }
